Package: RnwToRmd
Type: Package
Title: Knitr to R markdown converter
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Patrick Henaff
Maintainer: Patrick Henaff <pa.henaff@gmail.com>
Description: The function Rnw2Rmd converts a knitr file to a R markdown file.
    The conversion involves three steps:
    1/ insert the knitr R code into LaTex "verbatim"environments, so that the Rnw file is now pure LaTex code
    2/ use pandoc to convert the intermediate LaTeX file to a markdown file
    3/ convert the knitr code chunks to R markdown
Imports:
    knitr,
    stringr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
